window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Having finally completed the trials to join the Roaring Mountain, Casey has earned the support of the clan and access to their considerable resources. Both Maude and Magnus are backing him completely, encouraging Casey to do everything he can to be ready for the next challenge that comes along.</p> <p>At his back, he has two true friends. Einar Riggsson, the first drengr that Casey met in this world, and Vibeke Ylvasdottir, a fierce warrioress who has already proved a staunch ally through bloody conflict.</p> <p>With these friends to aid him, Casey is ready to see what opportunities await him within the borders of the Windsong Valley and the halls of the Roaring Mountain. But with the comforts and opportunities of a clan come the challenges of other drengr and the exterior threats that hunt them.</p> <p>On the horizon, a dark cloud rises. For each opportunity that awaits in this new place, a deadly threat readies its claws. Casey will have to show his true grit as a warrior if he is going to survive the challenges that await him.</p> <p><i>Steelforged Legacy </i>is a progression fantasy, men's romance, Western cultivation story that takes heavy inspiration from classic cultivation and combines it with an alternate take on Norse mythology. Even the gods can't always see the future right, and in this world, sometimes even the Fates can make mistakes.</p>"; 
